ivardefs.name: strength
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the degree of conformance expectations associated with this binding - that is, the degree to which the provided value set must be adhered to in the instances.

ivardefs.name: valueSet
ivardefs.desc: Points to the value set or external definition (e.g. implicit value set) that identifies the set of codes to be used.

properties.desc: Binds to a value set if this parameter is coded (code, Coding, CodeableConcept).
